data.description: "Welcome to your spacious 2-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom townhouse in desirable Upper Marlboro, MD! This multi-level gem features plush carpeting throughout, creating a cozy and inviting atmosphere. The heart of the home boasts a generous open kitchen with striking dark wood cabinets, providing ample storage and a sleek, modern look.  The owner's suite is a true retreat, complete with its own private bathroom, offering you a personal oasis within your home. Each of the bedrooms in this townhouse is spacious in size, providing comfort and flexibility for your living needs.  Enjoy the convenience of a deck located just off the living room, perfect for outdoor relaxation and entertaining. Plus, you'll love the added bonus of garage parking, making daily life even more convenient.  This townhouse is not only a comfortable abode but also conveniently located near shopping, entertainment, and major highways, providing easy access to all the amenities you desire. With 3 levels of living space, there's room for everyone to spread out and make this house their home. Don't miss this opportunity to own a townhouse that combines comfort, style, and a great location in Upper Marlboro. Schedule Your Showing TODAY!"
